      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oxford_Township%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "In 1835, Oxford Furnace pioneered America’s first successful use of the hot blast, dramatically cutting production time.",
